thread.title: Gregory Whitfield
thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by Gregory Whitfield

author: Gregory Whitfield
title: Gregory Whitfield
text:
Nice clean units with 24 hr access.
They need more flat bed carts to move your items to your unit.
There is a $10/month insurance fee which was not mentioned until it was time to sign the lease. So, they are getting an additional $10/month/unit with very, very little risk of having to ever pay out a claim.
